title: GDA delegation calls on PM
content:
ISLAMABAD, Jun 28 (APP):A delegation of Grand Democratic Alliance (GDA) Sunday called on Prime Minister Imran Khan.
The delegation included Minister for Inter Provincial Coordination (IPC) Dr. Fehmida Mirza and Saira Bano, MNA, PM office media wing in a press release said.
Separately, Ghulam Bibi Bharwana, MNA, also called on the prime minister.
